@jonasschnelli oops, I missed the README, I added a longer explanation there (longer than the one in the internal code documentation).

@MarcoFalke re #7466: the way I see it, the more useful feature of this script is renaming the files with commit ids and something else rather than just moving the binaries (which doesn't require much effort anyway).
Probably shorter versions of the commit ids would do as well (just the first X chars or ssomething).
